    <div id="app" data-server-rendered="true"><div class="theme-container"><header class="navbar"><div class="sidebar-button"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" role="img" viewBox="0 0 448 512" class="icon"><path fill="currentColor" d="M436 124H12c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12V80c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h424c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v32c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12zm0 160H12c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-32c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h424c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v32c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12zm0 160H12c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-32c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h424c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v32c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12z"></path></svg></div> <a href="/" class="home-link router-link-active"><!----> <span class="site-name">Maxie’s Notes</span></a> <div class="links"><div class="search-box"><input aria-label="Search" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" value=""> <!----></div> <nav class="nav-links can-hide"><div class="nav-item"><div class="dropdown-wrapper"><a class="dropdown-title"><span class="title">Languages</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></a> <ul class="nav-dropdown" style="display:none;"><li class="dropdown-item"><!----> <a href="/audio/dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg.html" class="nav-link">English</a></li><li class="dropdown-item"><!----> <a href="/ru/" class="nav-link">Русский</a></li></ul></div></div> <!----></nav></div></header> <div class="sidebar-mask"></div> <aside class="sidebar"><nav class="nav-links"><div class="nav-item"><div class="dropdown-wrapper"><a class="dropdown-title"><span class="title">Languages</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></a> <ul class="nav-dropdown" style="display:none;"><li class="dropdown-item"><!----> <a href="/audio/dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg.html" class="nav-link">English</a></li><li class="dropdown-item"><!----> <a href="/ru/" class="nav-link">Русский</a></li></ul></div></div> <!----></nav>  <ul class="sidebar-links"><li><section class="sidebar-group collapsable depth-0"><p class="sidebar-heading open"><span>Audio</span> <span class="arrow down"></span></p> <ul class="sidebar-links sidebar-group-items"><li><a href="/audio/edit-encoded-audio-with-ffmpeg-and-audacity.html" class="sidebar-link">Edit Encoded Audio with FFmpeg and Audacity</a></li><li><a href="/audio/downsample-audio-with-sox.html" class="sidebar-link">Downsample Audio with SoX</a></li><li><a href="/audio/dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg.html" class="active sidebar-link">DSD to PCM Conversion with FFmpeg</a><ul class="sidebar-sub-headers"><li class="sidebar-sub-header"><a href="/audio/dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg.html#conversion" class="sidebar-link">Conversion</a></li><li class="sidebar-sub-header"><a href="/audio/dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg.html#downsampling-with-sox" class="sidebar-link">Downsampling with SoX</a></li></ul></li></ul></section></li><li><section class="sidebar-group collapsable depth-0"><p class="sidebar-heading"><span>Kindle</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></p> <!----></section></li><li><section class="sidebar-group collapsable depth-0"><p class="sidebar-heading"><span>Privacy</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></p> <!----></section></li><li><section class="sidebar-group collapsable depth-0"><p class="sidebar-heading"><span>Proxy &amp; VPN</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></p> <!----></section></li><li><section class="sidebar-group collapsable depth-0"><p class="sidebar-heading"><span>Linux</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></p> <!----></section></li><li><section class="sidebar-group collapsable depth-0"><p class="sidebar-heading"><span>macOS</span> <span class="arrow right"></span></p> <!----></section></li></ul> </aside> <main class="page"> <div class="theme-default-content content__default"><h1 id="dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg"><a href="#dsd-to-pcm-conversion-with-ffmpeg" aria-hidden="true" class="header-anchor">#</a> DSD to PCM Conversion with FFmpeg</h1> <h2 id="conversion"><a href="#conversion" aria-hidden="true" class="header-anchor">#</a> Conversion</h2> <div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>ffmpeg -i audio.dsf -codec:a pcm_f32be -f f32be audio.pcm
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>In parallel:</p> <div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>find . -name &quot;*.dsf&quot; -print0 \
  | parallel -0 --tmux --eta \
      &quot;ffmpeg -i {} -codec:a pcm_f32be -f f32be {//}/{/.}.pcm&quot;
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br></div></div><p>DSD to PCM conversion results in a change to the sample rate. For example:</p> <ul><li><p>2.8224 MHz 1-bit DSD samples will be converted to 352.8 kHz PCM samples; and</p></li> <li><p>5.6448 MHz 1-bit DSD samples will be converted to 705.6 kHz PCM samples.</p></li></ul> <h2 id="downsampling-with-sox"><a href="#downsampling-with-sox" aria-hidden="true" class="header-anchor">#</a> Downsampling with SoX</h2> <div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>find . -name &quot;*.pcm&quot; -print0 \
  | parallel -0 --tmux --eta \
      &quot;sox --show-progress \
        -c 2 -r 705600 -e float -b 32 -B -t raw \
        {} \
        -b 24 -t flac -C 5 \
        {//}/{/.}.flac \
        rate -v 88200&quot;
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br></div></div><p>Or you may want to change bit depth to 16 bit:</p> <div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-text"><code>find . -name &quot;*.pcm&quot; -print0 \
  | parallel -0 --tmux --eta \
      &quot;mkdir -p {//}/sox-out ; \
       mkdir -p {//}/sox-out/logs ; \
       sox --show-progress \
         --guard \
         -c 2 -r 705600 -e float -b 32 -B -t raw \
         {} \
         -b 16 -t flac -C 0 \
         {//}/sox-out/{/.}.flac \
         rate -v 44100 \
         dither -s \
         2&gt;&amp;1 \
           | tee {//}/sox-out/logs/{/.}.sox.log&quot;
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br><span class="line-number">9</span><br><span class="line-number">10</span><br><span class="line-number">11</span><br><span class="line-number">12</span><br><span class="line-number">13</span><br><span class="line-number">14</span><br></div></div><br> <!----> <br> <div style="text-align:center;font-size:x-small;">
